## Status Bar

```js
"Toggle line numbers": {
    "command": "commands.toggleSetting",
    "args": {
        "setting": "editor.lineNumbers",
        "value": [
            "on",
            "off",
        ],
    },
    "statusBar": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "text": "ðŸ”¢",
        "priority": -9999,
    },
},
```

![status_bar](https://github.com/usernamehw/vscode-commands/raw/HEAD/img/status_bar.gif)


